strategies: I tried to think of real places i know of . Some of them  were familiar others sounded like they could exist . If the name was easy i chose that option.
familiar: Places i have been to or heard of because they are well known. example Hanover
memorable: If they had an easy spelling or i knew they existed.   Example Boulder city
unique: Complicated spellings.  EXAMPLE Sammamish ( located in washington state )
realistic: They sound as if they exist or i now they actually do exist.  Example Delaware city.
